        <span class="type"></span>?
      </div>
      </h1>  
    <p>Hi there! My name is Helen Fung. I'm currently working at <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/magnetic-asia-ltd" target="_blank" title="Linkedin Profile of Magnetia Asia">Magnetic Asia</a>.</p> 
